Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.33,0:00:16.67,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,110)\fad(1300,1500)\blur4}The Count of Monte Cristo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.70,0:00:06.99,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}So tonight I'll sing a song to all my friends
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:11.83,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Also to those we won't be seeing again
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.21,0:00:16.34,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}To those I knew and those I still adore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.05,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}And I want to see once more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.05,0:00:25.89,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}I just pray that you will love me and trust me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:30.73,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Laugh with me and cry with me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.10,0:00:35.77,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Spend those silent times with me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.90,0:00:39.90,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Love me ever more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.40,0:00:44.78,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Love me ever more
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:51.37,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}You and I were lovers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:55.33,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Our dreams were not soured by life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.54,0:01:01.09,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}And then my friends' betrayal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:08.35,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}Meant you never would be my wife
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.27,0:01:13.27,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}Harsh words were said
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:15.98,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}And lies were told instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.44,0:01:21.65,OP-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,500)}I didn't ever mean to make you cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:34.49,gankutsuou,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:39.12,gankutsuou,,0,0,0,,At Luna's Carnival, I encountered an immature soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.03,0:01:45.58,gankutsuou,,0,0,0,,My friend said to me, "This shall be the prelude to my vengeance."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:48.90,gankutsuou,,0,0,0,,But this soul was too young and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:53.84,gankutsuou,,0,0,0,,It is that alone which gives me cause for fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.97,0:02:02.97,count fo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}Act 2:\NUntil the Sun Rises Over the Moon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:16.26,count main,,0,0,0,,Are you going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:21.20,count main,,0,0,0,,That's enough fun and games, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:43.28,count main,,0,0,0,,I heard you met him the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:48.53,count main,,0,0,0,,Are you bored?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.70,count main,,0,0,0,,Not at all. It's a wonderful party, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.10,count main,,0,0,0,,Where is your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.47,count main,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Albert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:59.80,count main,,0,0,0,,He's probably out trying to pick up girls, and getting turned down by every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.91,0:03:02.88,count main,,0,0,0,,But this is terrible!\NThis is Luna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:06.31,count main,,0,0,0,,Strolling around alone at\Nnight is tantamount to suicide!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:07.68,count main,,0,0,0,,Surely you're exaggerating...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:12.82,count main,,0,0,0,,It's no laughing matter.\NYou'll get kidnapped by Luigi Vampa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:15.03,count main,,0,0,0,,Luigi Vampa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.40,0:03:17.33,count main,,0,0,0,,He's an up-and-coming bandit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:20.10,count main,,0,0,0,,They say that he drags his victims into the catacombs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.20,0:03:22.86,count main,,0,0,0,,...tortures them, and finally kills them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.00,0:03:24.33,count main,,0,0,0,,How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.77,count main,,0,0,0,,Surely the police won't stand by and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.84,0:03:28.27,count main,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.61,0:03:32.44,count main,,0,0,0,,The police on Luna arrange their patrols to avoid the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.75,0:03:39.38,count main,,0,0,0,,My very own cousin was robbed blind, had his arms and legs broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:42.45,count main,,0,0,0,,...and was left stark naked in the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:45.56,count main,,0,0,0,,All because he spoke to the bandit's mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:50.19,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's fine. I bet that he's back at your hotel at this very moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:51.90,count main,,0,0,0,,Would you care to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:59.43,count main,,0,0,0,,I simply despise when a party ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:04.10,count main,,0,0,0,,First one guest leaves, then two.\NEspecially at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.94,0:04:08.61,count main,,0,0,0,,You won't abandon me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.22,count main,,0,0,0,,Take him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.73,count main,,0,0,0,,You can't! It's mean!\NToday is my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.47,0:05:04.93,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Franz.\NI have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.50,count main,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:10.01,count main,,0,0,0,,Your father is leaving to see to some very important business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.34,0:05:13.24,count main,,0,0,0,,Fine, see if I care! I hope you never come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.96,0:05:25.42,count main,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:34.86,count main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.\NDid I keep you waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.86,count main,,0,0,0,,I... think I should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:47.31,count main,,0,0,0,,Are you Baron\NFranz d'Epinay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:51.45,count main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.92,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of your whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.59,0:05:57.56,count main,,0,0,0,,As for me, I killed ten people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:01.59,count main,,0,0,0,,This is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.39,count main,,0,0,0,,"My Lord Baron\NFranz d'Epinay."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:12.23,count main,,0,0,0,,"I, Luigi Vampa, have taken custody of your friend, the Viscount Albert Morcerf."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:17.18,count main,,0,0,0,,"Hand over the sum of 50 million ducats to my messenger immediately."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:20.34,count main,,0,0,0,,"If the messenger should not return by sunrise,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:24.04,count main,,0,0,0,,"...although it pains me to do so, think of your friend's life as forfeit."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:25.22,count main,,0,0,0,,Where is Albert?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:30.22,count main,,0,0,0,,He's a valuable hostage, so we're taking real good care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:35.02,count main,,0,0,0,,If the money is handed over, he'll be sent home without so much as a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:38.32,count main,,0,0,0,,You should have died!\NIs this how you people do things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.16,count main,,0,0,0,,Even I have a certain lifestyle to maintain.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.27,0:06:44.86,count main,,0,0,0,,50 million is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:49.20,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that a Parisian aristocrat won't be hard pressed to come up with such a sum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:52.44,count main,,0,0,0,,Dawn comes fast on Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:54.91,count main,,0,0,0,,If you value your friend's life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.54,count main,,0,0,0,,...I suggest that you make arrangements for the money as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:02.55,count main,,0,0,0,,I want to make an immediate withdrawal from the Bank of Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.66,0:07:04.15,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, sir,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.26,0:07:09.35,count main,,0,0,0,,...but our connection to Europe is currently offline due to solar winds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.96,0:07:11.43,count main,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything you can do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.43,count main,,0,0,0,,How much does sir require?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:44.09,count main,,0,0,0,,Albert... Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:50.13,count main,,0,0,0,,Say, son, it's awfully sad to see a young fella like yourself all alone on the last night of Carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.50,0:07:53.90,count main,,0,0,0,,If you want, I know a fine girl who...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.94,count main,,0,0,0,,Please, just be quiet and drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:02.14,count main,,0,0,0,,It was at my father's funeral that I first met Albert...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:24.93,count main,,0,0,0,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.40,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm not crying...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.36,count main,,0,0,0,,I'll play with you, so cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:30.50,count main,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone!\NGet lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.71,count main,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:46.69,count main,,0,0,0,,Ever since that day, Albert\Nand I have been inseparable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.23,count main,,0,0,0,,Damn! What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.22,0:09:20.32,count main,,0,0,0,,It's almost sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:24.39,count main,,0,0,0,,Have you raised the money yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:25.40,count main,,0,0,0,,Give me more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.86,count main,,0,0,0,,Once it's morning, I'll have the money transferred from Paris!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:32.60,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Luigi is a stickler for punctuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:38.23,count main,,0,0,0,,If you don't have the money ready by sunrise, your friend is a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.68,count main,,0,0,0,,Stop messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.71,count main,,0,0,0,,I suggest that you hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:47.01,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you don't want to see your friend die a horrible death, My Lord Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.29,0:09:48.31,count main,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:55.12,count main,,0,0,0,,Violence is unseemly,\NMy Lord Baron.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:57.86,count main,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:04.79,count main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's better. A gentleman has\Nto worry about little things like discretion.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:18.37,count main,,0,0,0,,There is no more fascinating spectacle than a man's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:25.28,count main,,0,0,0,,Yes, it almost feels as if one has become God, does it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:31.19,count main,,0,0,0,,His Excellency, the Baron d'Epinay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:36.63,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to disturb you at such an hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:42.74,count main,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?\NYou do not seem entirely well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.44,0:10:47.78,count main,,0,0,0,,Count! I have a favor to ask of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.06,count main,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:03.73,count main,,0,0,0,,There is your\N50 million ducats.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.96,0:11:06.76,count main,,0,0,0,,Now, you will take us to the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.21,count main,,0,0,0,,To the Colosseum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:36.66,count main,,0,0,0,,Have the two of you been friends for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:41.30,count main,,0,0,0,,Yes, we've been best friends since we were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.27,0:11:44.79,count main,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you are childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.63,count main,,0,0,0,,Constant friendship...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:51.94,count main,,0,0,0,,It is a wonderful thing, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.18,0:11:58.58,count main,,0,0,0,,Who do you like?\NC'mon, tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.55,count main,,0,0,0,,At least give me a hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:03.55,count main,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.43,count main,,0,0,0,,Luigi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.84,count main,,0,0,0,,It's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:24.81,count main,,0,0,0,,Kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:30.31,count main,,0,0,0,,So, have you made your peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.55,count main,,0,0,0,,C'mon, ma'am, let me kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:34.74,count main,,0,0,0,,No, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.34,count main,,0,0,0,,Oh, give it a rest, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:39.08,count main,,0,0,0,,You can carve him up as much\Nas you want after he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:44.59,count main,,0,0,0,,Now, then. You should put up a brave front while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:47.80,count main,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you'll sound like when you cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.00,count main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:13:00.58,count main,,0,0,0,,Um... Visitors to see the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:03.54,count main,,0,0,0,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.62,0:13:14.49,count main,,0,0,0,,Please, Teresa, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:16.72,count main,,0,0,0,,We can't kill him yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:19.20,count main,,0,0,0,,B-Because we won't get the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:22.56,count main,,0,0,0,,And besides... There's still a little time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:23.79,count main,,0,0,0,,Stand aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.90,0:13:25.56,count main,,0,0,0,,If you're going to use that, use it on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.97,0:13:28.34,count main,,0,0,0,,Squabbling among yourselves is pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.94,count main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NStand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:33.08,count main,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to disgrace the boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:35.58,count main,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:43.01,count main,,0,0,0,,So, does that mean you've fallen for that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:47.09,count main,,0,0,0,,That's so sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:51.43,count main,,0,0,0,,But she's too much for you to handle, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:57.80,count main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe... you'd rather become one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:04.50,count main,,0,0,0,,You know, I think I'll brand you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.75,count main,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:16.05,count main,,0,0,0,,Leave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:46.05,count main,,0,0,0,,I have come to meet with Signor Luigi Vampa, whose reputation is notorious on Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:47.72,count main,,0,0,0,,And who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:53.15,count main,,0,0,0,,My name is... Gankutsuou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:57.33,count main,,0,0,0,,T-The King of the Cave?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:01.22,count main,,0,0,0,,For one such as yourself who dwells in the darkness,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:04.16,count main,,0,0,0,,...I expect that I am better known by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.87,0:15:08.67,count main,,0,0,0,,I have your money.\NNow, hand over the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.11,0:15:11.34,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but you missed the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:15.48,count main,,0,0,0,,"Always be punctual," that's my motto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.32,0:15:20.84,count main,,0,0,0,,"Punctuality is the politeness of kings," is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.49,0:15:26.95,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm deeply honored... by your gracious words!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.07,0:15:44.17,count main,,0,0,0,,I see... Your skill is impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:49.25,count main,,0,0,0,,But you cannot kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:54.21,count main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you...\NAre you really...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:58.31,count main,,0,0,0,,A-Are you really him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.15,count main,,0,0,0,,I do not work for the authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.57,0:16:09.97,count main,,0,0,0,,If you would do me the honor of returning my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.53,count main,,0,0,0,,...all will be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.28,count main,,0,0,0,,You aren't injured, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:29.68,count main,,0,0,0,,I had a feeling that you would come to rescue me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.62,0:16:34.11,count main,,0,0,0,,If you wish to thank someone,\Nthank the good Baron d'Epinay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.89,0:16:37.89,count main,,0,0,0,,He was gravely concerned for your wellbeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:45.66,count main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.23,count main,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:54.17,count main,,0,0,0,,Say, I never asked you what your name was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:01.15,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm Albert.\NAlbert de Morcerf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:03.68,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm Peppo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:21.70,count main,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I was almost considering throwing in my lot with the bandits.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.18,0:17:26.20,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're all right, Albert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.11,count main,,0,0,0,,What took you so long, Franz?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.35,0:17:33.65,count main,,0,0,0,,I came this close to being killed, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.99,count main,,0,0,0,,I was seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:50.67,count main,,0,0,0,,What was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.77,0:17:57.50,count main,,0,0,0,,Please, do not concern yourselves over the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.94,count main,,0,0,0,,It served as a pleasant diversion for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:03.04,count main,,0,0,0,,But I have to do something to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:08.48,count main,,0,0,0,,In that case, might I ask one favor of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.62,count main,,0,0,0,,Anything at all!\NJust name it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:16.86,count main,,0,0,0,,I should like to take up\Nresidence in Paris at some point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.50,0:18:18.93,count main,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:24.60,count main,,0,0,0,,However, a rustic aristocrat such as myself has no connections in Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.14,0:18:30.40,count main,,0,0,0,,As such, might I impose on you to act as my intermediary into Parisian society?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.08,count main,,0,0,0,,Think nothing of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:40.01,count main,,0,0,0,,In that case, I shall call on you on\NMay 22nd, three months from this day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.98,count main,,0,0,0,,...to commemorate the events of this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.86,count main,,0,0,0,,Where in the world did you find this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:51.55,count main,,0,0,0,,I found it.\NAt the opera house.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.43,count main,,0,0,0,,Oh, so that is where it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:57.46,count main,,0,0,0,,It shames me to say it,\Nbut I have looked everywhere for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:19:00.17,count main,,0,0,0,,This, too, shows that there is some bond between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:04.00,count main,,0,0,0,,Please accept it with my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.18,0:19:07.08,count main,,0,0,0,,Think of it as a small token of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:09.24,count main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:12.48,count main,,0,0,0,,It will serve to freeze the memory of this day, this hour, in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:15.41,count main,,0,0,0,,A memory which belongs to us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.96,0:19:19.79,count main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!\NI'll cherish it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:25.82,count main,,0,0,0,,Carnival has ended, so what are your plans now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:30.50,count main,,0,0,0,,We're going to cut our trip short and take the evening shuttle back to Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:35.23,count main,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a minute!\NI've already made plans of my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:39.73,count main,,0,0,0,,You never learn, do you?\NAnd what "plans" might these be?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:43.54,count main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\NIt's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.15,count main,,0,0,0,,Have you arranged a rendezvous, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:50.71,count main,,0,0,0,,Sort of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.26,0:19:54.16,count main,,0,0,0,,Love is a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.96,0:19:58.90,count main,,0,0,0,,However, perhaps you have not noticed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:03.17,count main,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps you knew, and\Narranged the rendezvous regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:06.37,count main,,0,0,0,,I do hate to be the bearer of bad tidings, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:12.74,count main,,0,0,0,,A boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:14.67,count main,,0,0,0,,She's a boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.38,0:20:19.68,count main,,0,0,0,,Come out and say it! You think\NI'm an idiot, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.79,0:20:20.84,count main,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:24.08,count main,,0,0,0,,You're always looking down on me, laughing at me on the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.96,0:20:28.48,count main,,0,0,0,,I'm not laughing at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:32.42,count main,,0,0,0,,If I laughed at every boneheaded stunt you pulled, I'd bust a gut!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:35.23,count main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:39.84,count main,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.40,count main,,0,0,0,,I owe you my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.08,0:20:46.98,count main,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:07.66,count main,,0,0,0,,The fruits of betrayal must\Nbe plucked from the tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:15.79,count main,,0,0,0,,At long last, the appointed day arrives.\NHe comes to Paris along with a summer storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.66,0:23:19.16,count main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Gankutsuou,\NThe Count of Monte Cristo, act 3,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:20.16,count fo,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,525)}Act 3:\N5/22, Stormy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:21.39,count main,,0,0,0,,..."5/22, Stormy".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.53,0:23:23.56,count main,,0,0,0,,Bide your time, and hold out hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:57.70,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}I'm not the man I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:08.42,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}And what you see is not what it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.50,0:22:15.01,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}I traveled through space to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:23.64,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}What you don't know, you shouldn't fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:31.86,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}You won't see me coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.24,0:22:40.37,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}you won't see me coming
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.37,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}till I strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.26,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}You won't see me coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.68,0:23:05.77,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}you won't see me coming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.27,0:23:08.90,ED-English,,0,0,0,,{\blur7\fad(300,300)}till I strike!
